		<title>Quran&amp;#039;s Mathematical Mistakes in the inheritance Laws</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://atheism-vs-islam.com/index.php/divine-revelation-or-human-drama/166-quran-s-mathematical-mistakes-in-the-inheritance-laws"/>
