&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId604386&quot;&gt;(1) When SHARES make less than the Estate (An 'Asbah عصبة Case)&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId375244&quot;&gt;(2) When SHARES make MORE than the Estate (An 'Awl عول Case)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId111853&quot;&gt;(3) Linguistic Mistake in the Quran&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId964022&quot;&gt;Tehrif (Distortion) Case:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
