&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId307784&quot;&gt;(4) Kalalah كلالة: Contradictions in the Quran &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId519254&quot;&gt;(5) Quranists (The Rejectors of Hadith) making their own new Quran&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
