&lt;ul id=&quot;mozToc&quot;&gt;&lt;!--mozToc h1 1 h2 2 h3 3 h4 4 h5 5 h6 6--&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://atheism-vs-islam.com/#mozTocId604386&quot;&gt;(1) When SHARES make less than the Estate (An 'Asbah عصبة Case)&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
