&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.islamawakened.com/quran/4/st22.htm&quot;&gt;Pickthal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.islamawakened.com/quran/4/st64.htm&quot;&gt;Safi Kaskas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.islamawakened.com/quran/4/st38.htm&quot;&gt;Wahiduddin Khan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
